summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 1534, for the improvement of Lake Washington District of "North Trunk Sewer District" by constructing therein a main trunk sewer with certain branches; under Ordinance No. 16615 and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
